The '''Doiceşti Power Station''' is a large [[thermal power plant]] located in [[Doicești]], having 7 generation groups, 6 of 20 [[Watt#Megawatt|MW]] each and one of 200 MW resulting a total [[electricity]] generation capacity of 320 MW.<ref>[https://www.scribd.com/doc/3283429/Energomontaj-IEA-Bucuresti Centrala Termoelectrica Doiceşti]</ref> The power plant also has another 200 MW unit but it is decommissioned.

The chimney used by the 200 MW units is 208 metres tall.

