The '''White Hill Wind Farm''' is a [[wind farm]] in [[New Zealand]] operated by [[Meridian Energy]]. It was officially opened in 2007.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.scoop.co.nz/stories/AK0706/S00070.htm|title=South Island’s landmark first wind farm opened|date=2007-06-08|publisher=Scoop|accessdate=2008-09-26}}</ref>
